  "description" : "Amon is a young warrior on a desperate quest to avenge the death of his mother. When his hunt leads him to the castle of the Emperor Valhiss, Amon must endure the perils of initiation and join the ranks of the Imperial army in order to gain an opportunity to take his revenge. But once within the heart of the fortified city, Amon unexpectedly encounters the princess Lichia - the sultry daughter of King Sem Darai. The Emperor hopes to exchange the princess for a map in the King`s possession, but what is the Emperor`s ultimate goal?\nSet in a barbarous world of magic and mysticism and featuring character designs by the incomparable Yoshitaka Amano (Vampire Hunter D), Amon Saga is an action-packed tale of intrigue and adventure.\nNote: This video was shown theatrically on a double bill with http://anidb.net/a7076 [Itoshi no Betty Mamonogatari].",
